Take a look at our favorite jokes, then vote for yours at opinion.usatoday.com. USA TODAY Opinion_Eileen Rivers Our top picks for the best late-night laughs Samantha Bee (Photo: TBS)   
What's the one thing that President Trump isn't clamoring to put his name on? A health care bill that doesn't seem to include much of what he promised. 
Late-night comic Samantha Bee ranks the GOP replacement plan for Obamacare among other bills. See which bill was No. 1 (and why it's not Trumpcare) in Punchlines, above. 
And Saturday Night Live 's Michael Che tells us what coverage is missing for writers who need that extra boost to finish a screenplay. 
Take a look at our favorite jokes, then vote for yours in the quick poll to the right. Watching from your smartphone or tablet? Then visit opinion.usatoday.com to cast your ballot.
